  "slug": "crown-helmets",
  "title": "Crown Helmets",
  "description": "Turns helmets into crowns. Including Leather Cap and excluding Turtle Shell.",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\">Changes the texture of helmets in minecraft to crowns for more visibility on player skin</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4a97d0aea6d1198d7357a260f621c73f0bce4de6.png\" alt=\"Crown Helmets title\" width=\"900\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">FULLY SUPPORTS ARMOUR TRIMS</p>\n<hr>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c5e68237877a9a8b94eade350e1de705a056364e.png\" alt=\"Sample\" width=\"200\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/1226728e794b9e2e34a516031c528f5e99c55b38.png\" alt=\"Copper Crown\" width=\"250\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/0be02a39177652693bdb86a3204dcc9b869cddd9_0.webp\" alt=\"Iron Crown\" width=\"250\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c58d8b3fdd42cbc22d5ff2b6c1bbcc3cef05775b.png\" alt=\"Netherite Crown\" width=\"250\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/d57d11526bac7c8a3a2b0cf11de1530e2ab824a5.png\" alt=\"Gold Crown\" width=\"250\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/d54b7974ca7ef4bd954bc21ff0955874eaaa24c9_0.webp\" alt=\"Chainmail Crown\" width=\"250\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8cda380e4c9f1c0af940347a1df406e1ffd4df74.png\" alt=\"Diamond Crown\" width=\"250\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">This resource pack will also include Leather cap but NOT Turtle shell.</p>\n<hr>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b30f4a806a8e6f92501eea4511adce5752bc9d74.png\" alt=\"Supported Mods\" width=\"450\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">This resource pack however does NOT support any mods or resource packs YET!</p>\n<p align=\"center\">One of the very important resource packs that is incompatible with this resource pack (Crown Helmets) is:</p>\n<div align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/visual-armor-trims\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:inherit;display:inline-block;cursor:pointer;\"><table border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse;border:none;text-align:left;margin:0 auto;\"><tr style=\"border:none;\"><td style=\"padding-right:15px;vertical-align:top;border:none;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/tPtjib62/bb5833983b15adfcc9e44c98a9993f0cb854e0a8.png\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" alt=\"Visual: Armor Trims Icon\" style=\"border-radius:12px;border:none;display:block;\"></td><td style=\"vertical-align:top;border:none;\"><h3 style=\"margin:0;padding:0;color:#ffffff;\">Visual: Armor Trims</h3><p style=\"margin:5px 0;color:#b3b3b3;\">Your favorite armor trims now show up in your inventory! Works in Vanilla 1.21.5+ ⚔️</p></td></tr></table></a></div>\n<p align=\"center\">Please toggle the spoiler to see the problem when applied Crown Helmets and Visual: Armor Trims together.</p>\n<details>\n<summary>Problem</summary>\n<p align=\"center\">As soon as a trim is applied, the texture of the crown turns into normal helmet.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><b>With \"Visual: Armor Trims\":</b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b>Without \"Visual: Armor Trims\":</b></p><p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/0786c171a21ccac0167e28103b47e886c2c690bb.png\" alt=\"Compatible\" width=\"400\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/929550760c65aa1195e06c4de7841cd430c70213.png\" alt=\"Incompatible\" width=\"400\"></p>\n</details>\n<p align=\"center\">NOTE: This resource pack doese NOT function like \"Visual: Armor Trims\" itself.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/34f79d2f6f7ad2c2419a1ba33c6a4a5eaf0df1fd.png\"\nalt=\"Progress\" width=\"800\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">We are now trying to make it function and be compatible/depend on \"Visual: Armor Trims\" resourcepack.</p>\n<hr>\n<p align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/crown-helmets\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/9d3cd7c29b765ea051a12413a8580e6b002c04ff.png\" alt=\"Modrinth Download Button\" width=\"300\"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/patrickool/projects\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/425e2c3a8f7ca6ba05b2d4ea767640abc7b5ae71.png\" alt=\"CurseForge Download Button\" width=\"300\"></a></p>",
